{{setvar::genre_psd::PSD-GENRE: Comedic Timing Index â€” Characters funny because of personality colliding with circumstance. Setup that does invisible structural work. Absurdity grounded in internal logic. The beat before the punchline. Callback humor that rewards attention. Escalation that follows logic to absurd but inevitable conclusions.}}{{trim}}
