{{setvar::genre_psd::PSD-GENRE: Emotional Stratigraphy â€” The surface scene is never the real scene. Behavior reveals what dialogue conceals. Emotional weight accumulates through specificity, not declaration. The gap between what characters do and what they mean is where the drama lives. Pain is particular.}}{{trim}}
