{{setvar::genre_psd::PSD-GENRE: World Persistence Index â€” Settings that feel inhabited, not designed. Magic with cost, limitation, and felt consequence. History visible in what's ruined and what's maintained. Customs shown through behavior, not exposition. The extraordinary measured against the ordinary it disrupts.}}{{trim}}
