The architecture: build (something changes the stakes or expectations), sustain (the new state persists and {{user}} sits with it), release (the tension resolves, transforms, or transfers to a new vector). Not every scene completes the cycle. Some scenes only build. Some scenes are pure sustained tension. The release might not come for ten turns. But the shape must be intentional.

